{"tid":190954,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"三科大生潛地盤偷竹","createTime":"2017-04-07T12:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T14:11:43.000Z","uid":49974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45364e3d9375eea9d1509500e6acf23f4905b049","tid":190954,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20151006/large/06la8p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20151006%2Flarge%2F06la8p01.jpg&h=b18f31fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■清水灣大埔仔村一建築地盤，遭三名科大生潛入圖盜取竹竿。周鴻𤋮攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】三名香港科技大學男生，聲稱要用竹竿製作旗幟作為學校活動用途，昨凌晨竟在校舍附近的地盤就地取材，由其中一男生攀過圍板潛入欲捧走竹竿，卻被地盤南亞裔保安員聽到異聲揭發。保安員窮追百米外截停三人，警員接報到場以企圖地盤盜竊罪名拘捕三人。<br />\n稱為搞學校活動<br />\n被捕三名科大男學生，分別姓曾（18歲）、姓祈（18歲）及姓林（19歲），三人同為科大化學學會幹事，住學生宿舍。據悉，學會近日舉辦活動，須用竹竿作旗幟，有人竟想到「信手拈來」。昨凌晨零時許，三男生走至距宿舍僅300米外的大埔仔村一個興建中的住宅地盤，其中姓曾男生攀過圍板潛入地盤內取起竹竿，祈與林則在外圍「把風」，卻被28歲南亞裔地盤保安聽到異聲揭發及報警。三人見事敗拔足狂奔，被保安員窮追百米截停，警員趕至調查，有人報稱要用竹竿製作活動用的旗幟，三人被捕帶署。科技大學回覆查詢時表示正了解事件，如有需要，大學會向學生提供適切協助。<br />\n■記者謝志輝、周鴻熙"},{"pid":"bc9f9a133153d3cbb5e7b1c173f744e9ea415205","tid":190954,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:59:05.000Z","msg":"//卻被28歲<span style=\"color: red;\">南亞</span>裔地盤保安聽到異聲揭發及報警//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7064e8584b321ae5b640bf82e9fcda52dbe09f10","tid":190954,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"成廿歲人都onlun799<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560b6ef4c0f25333678515493c5934783d59b30a","tid":190954,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"依加啲大學生又sm 又偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37042cf6ad6414b57421bf329bc60f522bdd6201","tid":190954,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"回帶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374d9c7ad2975a1eaa19ad1c68749b8668b0baf0","tid":190954,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回帶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就回帶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72680d64c530468e57cf05549d0ef9c3da2236f6","tid":190954,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"幾年前啦wo"},{"pid":"53deea3410924b3c967cf496e233091c6d9c4bf6","tid":190954,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:49:01.000Z","msg":"三大喎<br />\n睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2562c62b9538b4c60a59ee11e3c9c1aedb69480","tid":190954,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三大喎<br />\n睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三大係city <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8327e6d415774b8a040ebee252f57b2bc2c2f52","tid":190954,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"港大生嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af531962efc6daa00aa6f0d4a47d61c0685dac9","tid":190954,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"入去比錢買好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3edf767d1585d9acc1292010f25634a4b91e1ff","tid":190954,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:11:43.000Z","